import React from 'react'
import {Grid, Typography} from '@material-ui/core'
import { useStyles } from './style'
import { Search, SubMenu } from '../'

const Equipment = props => {
  const classes = useStyles()
  const {items } = props
  return(
    <React.Fragment>
      <Grid container className={classes.root} spacing={2}>
        <Grid item xs={6}>
          <Search />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={6} pr={0}>
          <SubMenu items={[{id: 1, title: 'item 1', path: '/item_1'}, {id: 1, title: 'item 1', path: '/item_1'}, {id: 1, title: 'item 1', path: '/item_1'}]}/>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </React.Fragment>
  )
}

export {Equipment}
